{"badges":["TM31","TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place butter in mixing bowl and melt <nobr>2 min\/70°C\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Add milk, eggs, sugar, flour, baking powder and salt then mix <nobr>10 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>.","To cook pancakes, heat ½ tsp butter in a frying pan over a medium heat. For each pancake, pour in a ladle of batter and cook for 1-2 minutes or until bubbles appear on surface. Flip pancake over and cook for a further 1 minute. Transfer pancake to a serving plate and cover to keep warm. Repeat with remaining batter. Serve hot."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["50 g unsalted butter, plus extra for frying","300 g milk","2 medium eggs","30 g sugar","200 g plain flour","1 Tbsp baking powder (15 g)","½ tsp fine sea salt"]}],"id":"r178864","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-Jf5kW1XRBmw\/XZXYh7b8LpI\/AAAAAAAAf_M\/gbqxgNyBVaIjrT5tGzDjPcFziM_yzolHwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Oh97q9_0bIk2j88H.png","title":"American-style Pancakes","publishedAt":"2018-04-10T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"4 g","fat":"6 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"16 g","calories":"548 kJ \/ 131 kcal"},"usefulItems":"frying pan, ladle, hob","hintsAndTricks":["A popular choice when in need of a treat, these sweet, thick pancakes are whisked up in seconds with Thermomix®. For a savoury alternative, try the <i>Ham and Cheese Crêpes<\/i> on Cookidoo®.","Serve pancakes with maple syrup, whipped cream, chocolate, caramel sauce or jam.","To replace butter with oil, omit <nobr>step 1<\/nobr> and add <nobr>50 g oil<\/nobr> along with all other ingredients in <nobr>step 2.<\/nobr> Use oil instead of butter for frying.","<strong>Blueberry<\/strong> or <strong>raspberry pancakes<\/strong>: scatter <nobr>1 Tbsp berries<\/nobr> onto each pancake immediately after pouring batter into pan, before bubbles start to form.","<strong>Chocolate pancakes<\/strong>: add <nobr>2 tsp cocoa<\/nobr> powder in <nobr>step 2.<\/nobr>"],"basicInfo":["easy","40m","40m","12 pieces"]}